<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4, #34a853);
        color: #fff;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        padding: 48px 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        max-width: 480px;
        width: calc(100% - 32px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 32px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      form {
        text-align: left;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      form > * {
        width: 100%;
      }

      label {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        display: flex;
      }

      input[type='text'],
      input[type='email'] {
        width: 95%;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        color: #202124;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.15);
      }

      .roles {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top : 15px;
      }

      .role-option {
        flex: 1;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .role-option input {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
      }

      .role-option:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      button {
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 14px 20px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #202124;
        background: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 999px;
        cursor: pointer;
        width: 100%;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(32, 33, 36, 0.28);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrapper">
      <h1>추가 정보 입력</h1>
      <p>프로필 정보를 확인하고 필요한 항목을 채운 뒤 회원가입을 완료하세요.</p>
      <form action="/user/signup" method="POST">
        <label for="name">이름</label>
        <input
          id="name"
          name="name"
          type="text"
          value="<%= user ? user.displayName : '' %>"
          placeholder="이름을 입력하세요"
          required
        />
        <label for="email">이메일</label>
        <input
          id="email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          value="<%= user && user.email ? user.email : '' %>"
          required
          disabled = <%= true %>
        />
        <div>
          <label>회원 유형</label>
          <div class="roles">
            <label class="role-option">
              <input
                class="role-checkbox"
                type="checkbox"
                name="role"
                value="일반 사용자"
                checked
                <%= user && user.role === 'user' ? 'checked' : '' %>
              />
              일반 사용자
            </label>
            <label class="role-option">
              <input
                class="role-checkbox"
                type="checkbox"
                name="role"
                value="프로젝트 관리자"
                <%= user && user.role === 'manager' ? 'checked' : '' %>
              />
              프로젝트 관리자
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>        
        <input type="hidden" name="googleId" value="<%= user ? user.id : '' %>" />
        <button type="submit">회원가입 완료</button>
      </form>
    </main>
    <script>
      // Only allow one checkbox at a time.
      const boxes = document.querySelectorAll('.role-checkbox');
      boxes.forEach((box) => {
        box.addEventListener('change', () => {
          if (box.checked) {
            boxes.forEach((other) => {
              if (other !== box) other.checked = false;
            });
          }
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
